latestIgtvVideos.caption:
Summer Morning Skincare Routine ft. @uruoiskincare

Ad| With the hot and humid weather, my main focus is deep hydration and lightweight moisturization. The following products from their Glow Set help me achieve just that: 

Skin Lotion: a watery essence-toner with gentle anti-aging ingredients such as brown algae. This product preps my skin to better absorb the hydration from the following products in my routine.

Repair Essence: a viscous essence that is deeply hydrating. It contains sodium PCA, a wonderful humectant that also helps maintain a healthy skin barrier.

Moisture Milk: Lightweight but great at moisturizing and sealing in hydration. Works great under sunscreen in my am routine and under a thicker moisturizer during the colder months!

If you are interested in trying out any of their products or purchasing their sets, you can use my discount code LESLY15 for 15% off at checkout!

tbh I much prefer this as part of my makeup routine but I ain’t mad about that!

This is the @merit The Uniform Tinted Mineral Sunscreen

• shade 24 
• 15% zinc oxide
• SPF 45
• can be sheered out but if used as your main sunscreen, it has medium coverage 
• sets down to a velvety finish
• no fragrance

So while YES you can use this as your main sunscreen, it will take a bit longer to set down to that velvety finish. In the last clip, I had to go in with a brush (which affects the amount of coverage/sun protection) to get rid of the excess product that was sitting on my skin. This is why I much prefer it as a “skin tint” type of product! Actually love it for that purpose lol

as a back and side sleeper, a banana clip gives me the BEST results and also helps to add volume to my flat roots 🙂‍↕️

These are my day 3 curls and they still look bouncy on day 4! Even with a styling routine that offers me good hold, if I don’t protect it this way while I sleep my hair will not last and that’s just due to my curl pattern. 

Most nights I forget to put on my bonnet but with that said I still get really great results with just this clip + a good silk pillow case.

How do you protect your curls overnight? 💤😴

#overnightcurls #3acurls #curlyhairtips

guilty 🙋🏻‍♀️

Two things can be true at once: 
Doing my makeup early on in the day sets me up to be more productive. I don’t know what the psychology is behind it.. but once I get out of my pajamas and do a light glam, I am more likely to get those videos filmed and step out of the house to get those errands done ✔️ 

However.. at the same time..
It is a major method of distraction 😅 doing my makeup tricks my brain into thinking I’m being productive at something while in actuality I am delaying what actually needs to get done. This is not to say that I shouldn’t get cute for myself BUT it is to say that I should probably not spend as much time doing my makeup when there are more important things I need to get done asap 😩 

It really is a form of self care and avoidance haha

Are you also guilty of this? 

#makeuptherapy #softglam #sunkissedmakeup
